# .easignore — EAS Build arxiviga KIRMAYDIGAN fayllar.
# DIQQAT: bu fayl bo'lsa, EAS .gitignore o'rniga SHUNI ishlatadi — shuning uchun
# maxfiy fayllar va standart ignoralar ham shu yerda takrorlanadi.

# --- Bog'liqliklar va build artefaktlari (EAS build serverida qayta yaratiladi) ---
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.expo
**/.turbo
**/dist
**/build
*.tsbuildinfo
**/.vercel

# --- Maxfiy fayllar (EAS'ga hech qachon yuklanmasin) ---
**/.env
**/.env.*
*.local

# --- Loglar / OS / test natijalari ---
*.log
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
**/playwright/.cache

# --- Mobil build uchun keraksiz og'ir qismlar ---
marketing
